snippet.title: Character Demo - "Xianyun: Unfettered as the Wind" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
Though Cloud Retainer often speaks of her friends and disciples, and spends much time pondering the multifarious curiosities of the mortal world, she nonetheless claims to pass a life of freedom and leisure.
And indeed, you might ask, how else could she have invented all those wonderfully enigmatic mechanisms?
